        "body": "If you observe the most striking, visually arresting photographs in history—or the most iconic outfits ever worn on a red carpet—they all share a secret mathematical formula: Complementary Colors. In fashion styling, creating contrast using complementary colors is the equivalent of a visual explosion. When done incorrectly, you look like a walking billboard. When done correctly, you look commanding, highly creative, and utterly magnetic. Here is the optical science behind complementary styling and how to execute it perfectly."
